From f2ffc461856082c43fe7a0323e577fdc3f98a376 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: spike <s@s>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 14:25:12 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] KVM: arm64: add userspace stage-2 execute guard

Add an opt-in per-GFN dirty/XN, scanning/frozen, and approved/RX
state machine for Harmony AA-4. First execute exits before the
instruction. Writes revoke execute and exit before modification.
Userspace replies carry a non-reused scan generation.

Force PTE mappings, invalidate state on memslot and MMU-notifier
replacement, recheck under the fault lock, and serialize final
approval with mmu_lock. Reject nested/protected use and document the
trusted unique-backing/no-DMA boundary.

Signed-off-by: spike <s@s>
---
